{{Infobox sportsperson | name = Johannes Adam | fullname = | nationality = | residence = | birth_date = 1871 | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = | website = | country = | sport = [[Fencing]] | event = | collegeteam = | club = | team = | turnedpro = | coach = | retired = | coaching = | worlds = | regionals = | nationals = | olympics = | paralympics = | highestranking = | pb = | show-medals = yes }} '''Johannes Adam''' (born 1871, date of death unknown) was a German [[fencing|fencer]]. He competed at the [[1908 Summer Olympics|1908]] and [[1912 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ad/johann-adam-1.html |title=Johannes Adam Olympic Results |accessdate=2010-04-04 |work=sports-reference.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090725184111/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ad/johann-adam-1.html |archivedate=2009-07-25 |df= }}</ref>
